name: get_profile_series
description:
This is a sub-function API for tool outsystems_community_api.
Tool description: Get information about the OutSystems community. This is not an official OutSystems API.
API description: Fetches time series snapshots of a profile from the OutSystems Community API.

profile_id.description: The unique identifier of the profile for which the time series snapshots are to be fetched.
